g.text:
该部分分析Muduo网络库的定时器分析，属于level2级别，需要level1的基础#include <muduo/net/EventLoop.h>#include <muduo/base/Thread.h>#include <boost/bind.hpp>#include <stdio.h>#include <unistd.h>using namespace muduo;using namespace muduo::net;int cnt = 0;EventLoop* g_loop;void printTid(){ printf("pid = %d, tid = %d
", getpid(), CurrentThread::tid()); printf("now %s
", Timestamp::now().toString().c_str());}void print(const char* msg){ printf("msg %s %s
", Timestamp::now().toString().c_str(), msg); if (++cnt == 20) { g_loop->quit(); }}void cancel(TimerId timer){ g_loop->cancel(timer); printf("cancelled at %s
", Timestamp::now().toString().c_str());}int main(){ printTid(); sleep(1); { EventLoop loop; g_loop = &loop; print("main"); loop.runAfter(1, boost::bind(print, "once1")); loop.runAfter(1.5, boost::bind(print, "once1.5")); loop.runAfter(2.5, boost::bind(print, "once2.5")); loop.runAfter(3.5, boost::bind(print, "once3.5")); TimerId t45 = loop.runAfter(4.5, boost::bind(print, "once4.5")); loop.runAfter(4.2, boost::bind(cancel, t45)); loop.runAfter(4.8, boost::bind(cancel, t45)); loop.runEvery(2, boost::bind(print, "every2")); TimerId t3 = loop.runEvery(3, boost::bind(print, "every3")); loop.runAfter(9.001, boost::bind(cancel, t3)); loop.loop(); print("main loop exits"); }}

g.text: bool TimerQueue::insert(Timer* timer){ loop_->assertInLoopThread(); assert(timers_.size() == activeTimers_.size()); bool earliestChanged = false; Timestamp when = timer->expiration();//获取timer的超时时间 TimerList::iterator it = timers_.begin(); // TimerList timers_; // typedef std::set<Entry> TimerList; // typedef std::pair<Timestamp, Timer*> Entry; // timers_用于保存该定时器队列中的所有定时器 if (it == timers_.end() || when < it->first) {//如果当前定时器队列为空或者该定时器的超时时间比之前队列中的都早 earliestChanged = true;//设置“最早超时”定时器改变为真 } {//将该timer插入到定时器队列中，key是超时时间，value是定时器对象 //由于数据结构是set，所以定时器Entry对象不可能有重复 std::pair<TimerList::iterator, bool> result = timers_.insert(Entry(when, timer)); assert(result.second); (void)result; } { // ActiveTimerSet cancelingTimers_; // typedef std::set<ActiveTimer> ActiveTimerSet; // typedef std::pair<Timer*, int64_t> ActiveTimer; // static AtomicInt64 s_numCreated_; // 为什么会有这样一个集合？之前已经有timers_了，但是同一个时间戳可能会有不同的定时器Timer，这很正常，所以还需要一个pair，通过Timers对象的地址和序列号来标识这个Timer对象 std::pair<ActiveTimerSet::iterator, bool> result = activeTimers_.insert(ActiveTimer(timer, timer->sequence())); assert(result.second); (void)result; } assert(timers_.size() == activeTimers_.size()); return earliestChanged;}

g.text: //该函数直接获取超时的TimerEntry对象集合，然后将这些超时的Timer从队列中删除std::vector<TimerQueue::Entry> TimerQueue::getExpired(Timestamp now){ assert(timers_.size() == activeTimers_.size()); std::vector<Entry> expired; Entry sentry(now, reinterpret_cast<Timer*>(UINTPTR_MAX)); TimerList::iterator end = timers_.lower_bound(sentry); assert(end == timers_.end() || now < end->first); std::copy(timers_.begin(), end, back_inserter(expired)); timers_.erase(timers_.begin(), end); for (std::vector<Entry>::iterator it = expired.begin(); it != expired.end(); ++it) { ActiveTimer timer(it->second, it->second->sequence()); size_t n = activeTimers_.erase(timer); assert(n == 1); (void)n; } assert(timers_.size() == activeTimers_.size()); return expired;}

g.text: //有些定时事件是一次的，有些是循环定时执行的，但获超时的Timer已经从TimerQueue中移除了，所以这部分代码就是将这些需要反复循环执行的Timer再次加入到TiemrQueue中void TimerQueue::reset(const std::vector<Entry>& expired, Timestamp now){ Timestamp nextExpire; for (std::vector<Entry>::const_iterator it = expired.begin(); it != expired.end(); ++it) { ActiveTimer timer(it->second, it->second->sequence()); // ActiveTimerSet cancelingTimers_; if (it->second->repeat()//如果是需要被重复执行而且不在取消执行队列中 && cancelingTimers_.find(timer) == cancelingTimers_.end()) { it->second->restart(now);//重新计算并设置下一次触发的时间 insert(it->second);//将该Timer插入到TimerQueue中 } else { // FIXME move to a free list delete it->second; // FIXME: no delete please } } //如果TimerQueue中还有任务，那么将timerfd的超时时间(下一次触发读事件时间)设置为TimeQuene队列中最近被触发的Timer的时间戳 if (!timers_.empty()) { nextExpire = timers_.begin()->second->expiration(); } if (nextExpire.valid()) { resetTimerfd(timerfd_, nextExpire); }}

g.text: 8.总结（1）TimerQueue中持有一个timerfd和Channel，timerfd和Channel绑定。（2）TimerQueue持有一个Timer集合，每个Timer里都有定时触发的时间戳和处理函数。（3）TimerQueue和一个EventLoop关联，它的timerfd也被EventLoop中的Epoll/Poll监听。（4）TimerQueue的timerfd设置的发生读事件的时间是其内部Timer集合中最近超时的Timer的时间戳。（5）当timerfd发生读事件时，该时间之前的Timer集合中的超时时间Timer会被取出并执行超时时间函数。（6）超时的Timer会从TimerQueue中移除，如果是定时重复执行的Timer，则又会被加入到TimerQueue中。
